48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/7/72/Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg/1200px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F7%2F72%2FHong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg%2F1200px-Hong_Kong_Shue_Yan_University_logo.svg.png&h=3eb88b53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問過呢個未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d407e3f446b78949cd00efb7d3abd3e9764a302","tid":2500470,"uid":72085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1166c009d1fe9108664b90c526795d7465fc6b56","tid":2500470,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:08:05.000Z","msg":"個logo一啲誠意都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"拎嚟呃補助，咁認真做咩"},{"pid":"b0780c7f68ea3490697cd2563b3902c01d26ed42","tid":2500470,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:52:22.000Z","msg":"睇咗做難安<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc98f80e441ef950b082fd0193376006b1dddd9a","tid":2500470,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af20d43a9fcf6fb13b5e0869cee2f857356084e1","tid":2500470,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"中國官媒報導，中方計畫在河北省建立「雄安大學」，以清華大學、北京大學、復旦大學名校帶頭，還有南京大學、浙江大學、上海交大共35校共同參與創校，學校Logo在微博曝光後瘋傳，民運人士王丹認為是「史上最醜的Logo」，網友認為形狀像「兲」。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國官媒《人民網》、《中國教育在線》報導，中華人民共和國國務院副總理孫春蘭本月前往河北雄安新區，視察雄安宣武醫院、雄安新區啟動區大學園、「三校交鑰匙」項目施工現場，了解教育衛生支持雄安新區建設情況，事後指示集中規劃、建設雄安大學園區，促進融合發展；雄安大學預計2023年開始招生。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，目前北京大學、北京師範大學、中國傳媒大學等高校與雄安新區達成戰略合作協議。北京大學初步考慮將在雄安新區建立一流的醫學中心，北大光華管理學院在雄安新區開設分院。中國醫學科學院北京協和醫學院、中國地質大學（北京）、北京體育大學則將在雄安新區建設新校區。<br />\n<br />\n不過，雄安大學的Logo在網路曝光後，引發中國網友一片撻伐，有人認為「圖案看上去好像是身穿補服爬在地上磕頭的奴才」、「又使人聯想到『兲』字」、「的確容易產生誤會」；流亡美國的中國民運人士王丹也認為是「史上最醜的Logo」，許多其他國家的華文網友則抨擊「像極了跪舔」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3508685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3508685&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=35e9f969\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3508685&h=41d00d74\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3508685</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:53:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">屎弗向天？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3fb2c28123c2fcb57a1537c8a4112a1d384a78f8","tid":2500470,"uid":157411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:56:37.000Z","msg":"似向後掰大隻腳等比人屌"},{"pid":"f82b3a6d0e56c145519b418b095ffacb5bb4d774","tid":2500470,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"899701f6e7203888e51449ea294b9670caa3e855","tid":2500470,"uid":28195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T06:14:13.000Z","msg":"調轉180度睇下先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4rjbGFQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4rjbGFQ.png&h=c24e803a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:07:14.000Z","msg":"係跪係度呀"},{"pid":"4fc1c47ea7f368a54dfe99b8ecb1dac1d70fdc01","tid":2500470,"uid":59641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94d6b2296e83b8bdc554ebeb866cf1b3dd4e4cf1","tid":2500470,"uid":293376,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:07:35.000Z","msg":"個logo係咪唔對稱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畫果條友連AI都唔識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/